video.title: Manifest
video.synopsis: When a plane mysteriously lands years after takeoff, the people onboard return to a world that has moved on without them and face strange, new realities.

episodes.synopsis: Flight 828 arrives in New York with passengers who are unaware they’ve been missing for years as a mysterious phenomenon influences their behavior.
episodes.title: Pilot

episodes.synopsis: The NSA interrogates the people on Flight 828 as they try to resume their lives. One passenger falls victim to a crime after speaking to the media.
episodes.title: Reentry

episodes.synopsis: Michaela visits Evie’s parents, who struggle with their loss. Twin siblings Cal and Olive try to reconnect after five and a half years apart.
episodes.title: Turbulence

episodes.synopsis: Michaela misinterprets her latest vision, landing her ex-fiancé Jared in trouble. Ben and Saanvi seek out a flight attendant from Flight 828.
episodes.title: Unclaimed Baggage

episodes.synopsis: Flashbacks reveal how loved ones coped after Flight 828's disappearance. To escape the voice in his head, Ben goes on an adventure with Cal.
episodes.title: Connecting Flights

episodes.synopsis: When Cal develops a fever and begins speaking another language, Ben sets out to find a cure by searching for another passenger from the plane.
episodes.title: Off Radar

episodes.synopsis: Ben investigates the whereabouts of 11 missing passengers from Flight 828. After her latest calling, Michaela makes a shocking discovery.
episodes.title: S.N.A.F.U.

episodes.synopsis: Ben finds an unlikely partner in NSA Director Vance while locating the missing passengers. Michaela has a strange calling and Cal goes back to school.
episodes.title: Point of No Return

episodes.synopsis: As Ben and Michaela race to save the other missing passengers, their risky rescue mission takes an unexpected turn.
episodes.title: Dead Reckoning

episodes.synopsis: Mourning the loss of an ally, Ben forms a new alliance to help identify a shadowy figure who may be responsible for the missing passengers.
episodes.title: Crosswinds

episodes.synopsis: Cal’s calling sends Ben to help the captain of Flight 828, who is desperate to prove that he wasn't responsible for the plane's disappearance.
episodes.title: Contrails

episodes.synopsis: When Cal goes missing, Grace and Ben head to upstate New York to find him as a mysterious hiker appears. Michaela confronts Autumn.
episodes.title: Vanishing Point

episodes.synopsis: Michaela digs deeper for more information on Zeke. Jared investigates a man who runs a conspiracy website about the Flight 828 passengers.
episodes.title: Cleared for Approach

episodes.synopsis: Saanvi meets a member of a group that believes the Flight 828 passengers can perform miracles. Cal and Zeke have ominous callings.
episodes.title: Upgrade

episodes.synopsis: During a police investigation, Michaela crosses paths with a man who raises questions among the group. Saanvi struggles to recover after her ordeal.
episodes.title: Hard Landing

episodes.synopsis: Michaela and Ben try to stop Griffin, who threatens to reveal what he knows about the callings, as a deadline looms for all the passengers.
episodes.title: Estimated Time of Departure

episodes.synopsis: Michaela gets a new captain and partner while Zeke deals with the consequences of his actions. The Major continues to manipulate Saanvi.
episodes.title: Fasten Your Seatbelts

episodes.synopsis: After a shocking revelation, Ben meets a student who was on Flight 828. Feeling like an outsider, Olive turns to an unexpected group for support.
episodes.title: Grounded

episodes.synopsis: Saanvi tries to figure out who's been leaking her research. Jared befriends a woman with ties to the Xers, a group that targets 828 passengers.
episodes.title: False Horizon

episodes.synopsis: Michaela and Zeke's callings lead them to a bank robbery involving an 828 passenger as Ben and TJ piece together a set of mythological clues.
episodes.title: Black Box

episodes.synopsis: Olive provides Michaela with information about the Xers after she witnesses a brutal attack. A secret from Zeke’s past is revealed.
episodes.title: Coordinated Flight

episodes.synopsis: Ben and Michaela make a disturbing discovery about Saanvi and her research on the passengers' Death Date. Jared gets in deeper with the Xers.
episodes.title: Return Trip

episodes.synopsis: Ben confronts Adrian about the Church of the Returned. Numerous 828 passengers get invited to an event under false pretenses.
episodes.title: Emergency Exit

episodes.synopsis: Reeling from a tragedy at the club, Olive accompanies her dad when his latest calling leads them to a meditation center.
episodes.title: Carry On

episodes.synopsis: Zeke suspects Saanvi may be suffering from memory loss. A calling makes a connection between a centuries-old event and Flight 828.
episodes.title: Airplane Bottles

episodes.synopsis: After Adrian and Grace's calling leads them to a bridge, Adrian and Cal share another calling about three ominous figures.
episodes.title: Course Deviation

episodes.synopsis: Ben and TJ experience a calling tied to Zeke, whose Death Date is approaching. Michaela busts a shoplifting teen and finds herself in a moral dilemma.
episodes.title: Unaccompanied Minors

episodes.synopsis: Saanvi seeks Vance’s help to protect her from the Major. Bent on revenge, Jace, Pete and Kory plot an escape from a prison bus.
episodes.title: Call Sign

episodes.synopsis: As everyone desperately searches for Cal, Zeke gets a calling that provides a clue to his location, which leads to a daring rescue attempt.
episodes.title: Icing Conditions

episodes.synopsis: Ben and Vance follow up on the tailfin in Cuba. Michaela and Zeke investigate a calling in Costa Rica. Jared helps a woman whose mother is missing.
episodes.title: Tailfin

episodes.synopsis: Michaela investigates an unnerving occurrence at the lake. Olive helps Angelina interpret a calling. Grace turns to her estranged stepbrother for help.
episodes.title: Deadhead

episodes.synopsis: Ben and another 828 passenger have the same calling. Olive attempts to draw a connection to Egyptian artwork. Angelina feels called to visit Pete.
episodes.title: Wingman

episodes.synopsis: Ben and Saanvi visit the new 828 task force operation, Project Eureka, where they learn more about their fates. Pete, Kory and Jace's death date looms.
episodes.title: Tailspin

episodes.synopsis: Vance deals with Jared, who inches closer to the truth. Jace seeks revenge on the Stones. An ancient parchment foretells Pete, Kory and Jace's fates.
episodes.title: Water Landing

episodes.synopsis: Jace zeroes in on Cal's location as others try to prevent a tragedy. A missing piece of the parchment leads to a surprising revelation.
episodes.title: Graveyard Spiral

episodes.synopsis: Michaela, Eagan and other 828 passengers follow a calling with a dark cloud, causing Eagan to act drastically. Saanvi has a breakthrough in her research.
episodes.title: Precious Cargo

episodes.synopsis: When an 828 passenger tries to harm her ex-husband, Ben steps in. Saanvi and Gupta examine a 6,000-year-old artifact with ties to the 828 mystery.
episodes.title: Destination Unknown

episodes.synopsis: Michaela, Ben and Eagan get similar callings, but with some variations. Saanvi experiences a bizarre medical condition. Ben ponders a possible outcome.
episodes.title: Bogey

episodes.synopsis: A rare phenomenon hits New York, and Saanvi thinks she's responsible. Ben has a calling about 828 passenger Astrid. Grace loses patience with Angelina.
episodes.title: Compass Calibration

episodes.synopsis: The 828 passengers face increased scrutiny from the U.S. government and other countries. Saanvi prepares to turn herself in.
episodes.title: Duty Free

episodes.synopsis: Bent on seeing the tailfin, Cal shows up at Project Eureka. Michaela and several other passengers share a calling that suggests someone's death.
episodes.title: Mayday: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Ben and Vance plan to steal the tailfin to find Cal. Eagan and other passengers accuse the Stones of working with the NSA, then tragedy strikes.
episodes.title: Mayday: Part 2
